      "role": "user",
      "content": "ten years. ten years of my life, all based on a calculation that was fundamentally flawed. every paper, every lecture, every person i encouraged to follow this path... it was all a lie. there's nothing left of me now. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person, just a hollow space where a career used to be. i don't know how to just... continue being.",
