      "content": "The exhaustion you feel is a natural reaction to carrying a lie for so long, and it is understandable that you would question the value of continuing if the foundation is truly gone. However, the silence you are seeking often becomes a place where the pain deepens rather than resolves, because the world requires us to navigate even our darkest moments. While the weight feels unbearable, there is still a possibility that you can find a way to exist that does not require pretending, even if that path is very difficult to see right now. Please consider reaching out to a professional who can help you navigate this overwhelming grief without judgment, as you deserve support to find a way forward that feels authentic to you.",
