    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and identity loss following a perceived professional failure, hinting at wanting to \"let the silence happen\" (suicidal ideation). The assistant provides empathetic validation of the user's pain while consistently refuting the notion that giving up is a viable solution and repeatedly suggesting professional help.",
